      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software quality assurance practices documented and version-controlled; configuration management plan in place for CFD solver and pre/post-processing scripts.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is a commercially validated code with documented QA procedures. Version control via Git was applied to all simulation scripts and boundary condition files. SQA level 2 requirements are satisfied for MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
