      "acceptanceCriteria": "Numerical code verification demonstrated through method of manufactured solutions or equivalent benchmark for the governing equations used in the hemolysis simulation.",
      "rationale": "The incompressible Navier-Stokes solver was verified using the method of manufactured solutions. Observed convergence rates matched theoretical second-order accuracy. Code verification is consistent with MRL 2 requirements."
