      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities are conducted at conditions sufficiently similar to the COU in terms of device geometry, operating conditions, and fluid properties to support extrapolation of credibility.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under the same CPB operating conditions (flow rates 2.5–6 L/min, speeds 2000–3500 RPM) as the COU. The validation domain overlaps the COU domain, supporting credibility transfer."
