      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2; nominal input values are well-characterized from device specifications and standard fluid property databases.",
      "rationale": "Geometric inputs are derived from certified manufacturing drawings. Fluid properties (viscosity, density) are taken from ASTM F1841 reference values. Input uncertainty propagation is not required at MRL 2 for comparative hemolysis assessment."
