    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out under MRL 2 provisions. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all 5 operating points. Project requirements documented in the credibility plan have been addressed through the structured factor assessments and validation activities. The credibility assessment team accepts this model for the stated COU.",
